data.description: “Completely remodeled turnkey modern spacious ranch home with 5 bedrooms and 3 baths.  Brand new stainless steel appliances in a bright and airy kitchen and dining.  Beautiful living room with fireplace and large windows with great natural lighting.  Fantastic basement, fully carpeted with windows and recessed  lighting.  Has 2 bedrooms, bathroom and large recreational area.
data.whatILove: What I like best about this home is that everything inside is sparkling brand new. Everything has been completely remodeled including all the doors and windows. Really there is absolutely nothing that needs to be done. It is priced right to allow landscaping of choice.
